#: ../../source/opac.rst:850
msgid "If your patrons would like to see the items barcodes on their list of checked out items you can set up a :ref:`patron attribute <patron-attribute-types-label>` with the value of SHOW\\_BCODE and :ref:`authorized value <authorized-values-label>` of YES\\_NO."
