msgid "|image1010|"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/opac.rst:900
msgid "Patrons can cancel or suspend (depending on the value of your :ref:`SuspendHoldsOpac` system preference) their own holds if they are not in transit or already waiting for them. When they click 'Suspend' they will be presented with the option to choose a date for their hold to resume."
