#: ../../source/opac.rst:1206
msgid "If the :ref:`TranslateNotices` preference is set to Allow the patron will also see an option to choose 'Preferred language for notices' with a dropdown list of available languages."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/opac.rst:1211
msgid "You must choose a delivery method (SMS or email or phone) along with 'Digest only?' if you would like to receive a digest of the messages."
