#: ../../source/opac.rst:1259
msgid "Your interlibrary loan requests"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/opac.rst:1261
msgid "If your library has the :ref:`ILLModule` preference set to ‘Enable’ patrons will have the option to make ILL requests when logged in to their OPAC account.  From here they can view their existing requests and place new ones."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/opac.rst:1265
msgid "|image1373|"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/opac.rst:1267
msgid "To place a new interlibrary loan request click on ‘Create a new request’ and choose a request form."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/opac.rst:1270
msgid "|image1374|"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/opac.rst:1274
msgid "The options displayed are dependent on your ILL configuration.  See the ILL backends wiki page at https://wiki.koha-community.org/wiki/ILL_backends further explanation."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/opac.rst:1280
msgid "If you have entered copyright text in the :ref:`ILLModuleCopyrightClearance` preference the text displays here and you need to click ‘Yes’ to accept before continuing."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/opac.rst:1284
msgid "Complete the publication details as fully as possible. Depending on the form in use you may see the option to add Custom fields for additional information such as notes.  Destination branch is a required field, this is the branch you would like the request to be sent to."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/opac.rst:1289
msgid "|image1375|"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/opac.rst:1291
msgid "Click on 'Create' to submit your request to the library for processing."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/opac.rst:1293
msgid "Your submitted request will be listed with a status of ‘New request’.  Once processed the status will be updated to ‘Requested’."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/opac.rst:1296
msgid "Click on ‘View’ to make changes or cancel your request."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/opac.rst:1298
msgid "You cannot edit the form details but you can add a note to request a modification and then click on ‘Submit modifications’ at the bottom of the screen.  Your modification will be sent to the library for processing."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/opac.rst:1302
msgid "For new requests you will also have the option to ‘Request cancellation’. Your request will be updated with the status ‘Cancellation requested’ and can then be removed by library staff."
msgstr ""

